#: ../../source/auth/mfa.rst:2
msgid "多因子认证"
msgstr "Multi-Factor Authentication"

#: ../../source/auth/mfa.rst:3
msgid "多因子认证是在单因子认证不足以保证安全性时使用的方法，通常会引入多种方式对用户身份进行验证。身份验证方法可以基于知识的认证，即密码；也可以基于物品的认证，例如硬件密钥；也可以是基于特征的认证，例如包含指纹在内的生物特征等。"
msgstr ""
"Multi-factor authentication is used when single-factor authentication is not "
"sufficient to ensure security. It usually introduces multiple methods to "
"verify a user's identity. Authentication methods can be knowledge-based, such"
" as passwords; possession-based, such as hardware keys; or characteristic-"
"based, such as biometrics including fingerprints."

#: ../../source/auth/mfa.rst:5
msgid "具体来说，目前常用的生物特征有：指纹、人脸、虹膜、静脉、声纹、体态等。常用的评价指标主要是速度（注册、识别使用的时间），精确度（假阳性、假阴性）等。"
msgstr ""
"More specifically, commonly used biometric characteristics include "
"fingerprints, face, iris, vein patterns, voiceprints, and gait. Common "
"evaluation metrics mainly include speed, such as the time required for "
"enrollment and recognition, and accuracy, such as false positives and false "
"negatives."
